        ("Ordered list", "Generate ordered list", code("ol")),
        ("Table", "Generate markdown table", code("table")),
      )
    )
  ),
  h1("Example:"),
  p(
    "Example of usage, you can find ", a("here.", "./src/Readme.sc")
  )
